      <title>以色列允许暂停脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动在加沙开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-as-israel-allows-pauses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周前，加沙地带一名 10 个月大的婴儿被诊断出患有脊髓灰质炎这种导致瘫痪的疾病。周日，加沙地带启动了针对儿童的脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-as-israel-allows-pauses</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:00:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民粹主义者崛起，舒尔茨执政联盟在德国选举中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/scholz-coalition-crushed-in-two-state-votes-as-populists-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟在德国东部的两次地区选举中遭遇惨败，极右翼和极左翼的民粹主义政党在图林根州和萨克森州分别赢得了约一半的选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/scholz-coalition-crushed-in-two-state-votes-as-populists-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 16:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯坦吉·布朗·杰克逊法官正在四处宣传她的新回忆录《可爱的人》</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-01/justice-ketanji-brown-jackson-is-hitting-the-road-to-promote-her-new-memoir-lovely-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——最高法院法官凯坦吉·布朗·杰克逊正在全国范围内进行高调巡演，宣传她的新回忆录《可爱的人》。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-01/justice-ketanji-brown-jackson-is-hitting-the-road-to-promote-her-new-memoir-lovely-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 14:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列工党宣布发动袭击以迫使以色列达成人质协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/israel-labor-union-declares-strike-to-press-for-hostage-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方在加沙地带找到六名人质尸体后，以色列劳工联合会（Histadrut）周日宣布全国罢工，以向总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的政府施压，要求其与哈马斯达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/israel-labor-union-declares-strike-to-press-for-hostage-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 14:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国马克龙将在任命新总理前与前社会党人卡泽纳夫会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/france-s-macron-to-meet-ex-socialist-cazeneuve-before-naming-new-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将于周一会见前社会党高级官员、曾担任总理的贝尔纳·卡泽纳夫，这位法国总统即将宣布谁将成为下一任总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/france-s-macron-to-meet-ex-socialist-cazeneuve-before-naming-new-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 13:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管对哈里斯的计划存在疑问，但她仍找到了劳工界最重要的盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/harris-finds-allies-in-labor-leaders-despite-questions-on-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯希望工会的支持能帮助她在 11 月大选中获胜。尽管她还没有明确说明她将如何追随这位被誉为几代人以来最亲近工人的总统，但工会领袖们正纷纷表示愿意支持她。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/harris-finds-allies-in-labor-leaders-despite-questions-on-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿塞拜疆执政党在议会提前选举中赢得大多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/election-in-azerbaijan-s-ruling-party-is-set-to-extend-its-grip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据除三个选区外所有选区进行的出口民意调查显示，阿塞拜疆执政党新阿塞拜疆党在周日的提前选举中赢得了该国议会最多席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/election-in-azerbaijan-s-ruling-party-is-set-to-extend-its-grip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫斯科炼油厂发生火灾后，俄罗斯对哈尔科夫体育中心进行空袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/fire-at-moscow-oil-refinery-as-russia-downs-158-ukrainian-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯称，其一夜之间在十多个地区击落了 158 架乌克兰无人机，其中包括首都，那里的一家大型石油加工厂因无人机袭击而起火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/fire-at-moscow-oil-refinery-as-russia-downs-158-ukrainian-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人质死亡事件引发愤怒，内塔尼亚胡坚持谈判立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/biden-says-6-hostages-bodies-recovered-including-us-citizen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列发现了六名人质的尸体，据称这些人质是在加沙被哈马斯绑架者杀害的，这促使以色列最大的工会发起罢工，向总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡施压，要求其与巴勒斯坦激进组织达成停火协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/biden-says-6-hostages-bodies-recovered-including-us-citizen</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 04:02:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>家人确认以色列裔美国人质戈德堡-波林已死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-01/urgent-family-confirms-death-of-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——周日晚上，加沙又有六名人质被发现死亡，悲痛和愤怒的以色列人涌上街头，高呼“现在！现在！”，要求总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯达成停火协议，将剩余的俘虏带回国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-01/urgent-family-confirms-death-of-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 03:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
